<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="J" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Joyful" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Joyful,</orth> 1) glad, feeling happy: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 1.1.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. I, 1, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.1.80" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 1, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 2, 29</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.143" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A III, 1, 143</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.203" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 7, 203</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.99" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.2.6" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 2, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 4.2.93" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 3, 51</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.116" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.4.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 4, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.116" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.116" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 116</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.4.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 4, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.402" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 402</bibl>. <emph>j. tears</emph> == tears of joy: <bibl n="shak. h8 5.3.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 V, 3, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 4.8.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. IV, 8, 9</bibl>. With <emph>of</emph>: <cit><quote>j. of your reformation,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.879" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 879</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>j. of thy company,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.5.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 5, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>of your sights,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.255" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 255</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) glad, making happy: <cit><quote>the j. day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 5.3.1" default="NO" valid="yes">As V, 3, 1</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.3.131" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 3, 131</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 6</bibl>. <cit><quote>j. tidings,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 1, 35</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.105" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 2</bibl>. <cit><quote>j. births,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 35</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a j. issue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. IV, 2, 66</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a j. trouble,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 2.3.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 3, 53</bibl></cit>.
